<p style="text-align:center;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">
	<span class="img_descr" style="line-height:2;font-size:12px;color:#333333;">BENGIBBSPHOTOGRAPHY.COM</span>
</p>
<p style="font-size:18px;font-family:&quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;">
	<span style="line-height:2;">　　</span><strong><span style="line-height:2;">Edythe L。 and Eli Broad（美国-洛杉矶）</span></strong>
</p>
<p style="font-size:18px;font-family:&quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;">
